  * Cash denomination buttons: increased height to `28px` with an `11px` font size (much more touch-friendly).
  * Split payment inputs (Cash, UPI, Card, Due): increased input heights to `26px` with a `13px` font size.
* **Auto-Dismiss & Close Handlers**:
  * Tapping the close button (`&times;`) in the top-right corner of the popover instantly closes it.
