          <label class="remember" style="margin-bottom:18px"><input type="checkbox" id="reg-terms" required> I agree to the <a href="#" style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:600">Terms</a> &amp; <a href="#" style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:600">Privacy Policy</a></label>
